---
title: Southwestern Beef Burgers with Spiced Potato Wedges
description: Tonight is right for a kickin' western-style burger. Monterey Jack cheese melts over Southwestern spiced beef patties and smoky seared poblanos and onions, with a slathering of garlic mayo to bring it all together. On the side, there’s a heap of garlicky oven fries, because you deserve it.
